bpm.gateway.core.server.userdefined
Class Parameter

java.lang.Object
  bpm.gateway.core.server.userdefined.Parameter

public class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object

This class is for define a Parameter for the Parameter. The Parameetr value can be used inside Transformation as name for file output, or as value on some Transformation(Calculation, Filters, ...)
